column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/p4957_13d76e5cdca2ba8382ecbf91790ef89dcc74a6ac/ for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated.
